m are all shaped on well planned, SEO friendly fabrications.</p>\n<p>Recently, we conducted a short review among our fellow employees. We asked a list of questions to analyze what does a good hosting platform really needs.</p>\n<p>Should a WordPress hosting provider be your partner in managing your WordPress website? Should a hosting provider be responsible to give you peace of mind while hosting with them?</p>\n<p>The reply came out to be an astounding yes! but the truth of WordPress hosting industry these days is that they can give you more trouble than ease while hosting your business sites with them.</p>\n<h2>We Found Cloudways &#8211; A Managed Cloud Hosting Platform</h2>\n<p><a href="http://www.cloudways.com">Cloudways</a> is one of a kind, managed cloud hosting platform and believe it or not, it does offer what it claims. They are your Managed WordPress hosting provider that you can rely on, their servers are highly reliable, their support is interactive and quick, they literally apply no restrictions on your WordPress websites, and best of all moving to their hosting servers is easy as clicking a few buttons.</p>\n<p>Here are some of the features why we, at SeedProd, believe that Cloudways is the best managed hosting solution for you!</p>\n<h2>The Ultimate Mix of Advanced Caching Technologies</h2>\n<p>They say that your first impression is your last impression! When we landed on the homepage of Cloudways, we found out that they give layers of advanced caching technology that guarantees consistent website uptime and incredible performance. So, it lead us to creating an account at Cloudways, and to much of our surprise, it all came out pretty true.</p>\n<p>Without a doubt Cloudways&#8217; stack is something that even premium hosting providers fall short of providing. Setting up WordPress and using advanced caching services like Varnish, Redis, Memcached is not intimidating at all, as they provide it by default.</p>\n<p>A Truly Managed WordPress Hosting Provider &#8211; Zero Server Maintenance Required</p>\n<p>As we are all pretty aware of the fact, hosting platforms on cloud servers can become a tedious task. It requires plenty of efforts to launch and maintain a WordPress website. Above that, rolling out application updates and keeping track of your server maintenance can equally become troublesome.</p>\n<p>But with Cloudways, you can put all your hosting hassles aside. You get a ready WordPress application with a preconfigured account and all you will ever have to do is just log into your application. No more investing time on server maintenance because experts at Cloudways do it for you saving you a lot of time so that you can focus on building better websites for your clients</p>\n<p>Here is how you can launch your <a href="https://www.cloudways.com/blog/host-wordpress-on-digitalocean/">WordPress application on Cloudways</a>.</p>\n<h2>No Plugin Restrictions</h2>\n<p>Although, WordPress market is quite vast and you have the flexibility to add as many themes and plugins you want.</p>\n<p>Other Managed hosting providers won&#8217;t let you install your favorite or new WordPress plugins, they will limit you so they don&#8217;t have to fix the compatibility issues that you might run into.</p>\n<p>On Cloudways, the case is a bit different. You can try out any WordPress plugin on your website and Cloudways won&#8217;t stop you from using it.</p>\n<p>Think about the freedom they provide, you can build any type of website while hosting with them.</p>\n<p>On the other hand, unlike other managed cloud hosting providers, Cloudways doesn’t restrict you to using a large number of plugins. You can freely select as many plugins as you want. It gives you the liberty to organize, maintain and add many features to your WordPress website.</p>\n<h2>Fairest Pricing Plans</h2>\n<p>Most managed hosting providers  come with a preplanned pricing package that are expensive to most users. Most of the time, you are not really well aware of what you are exactly being charged for? Although we found out that Cloudways follow a simple pricing model; however, they added a bit of flexibility to it. They follow as they call it, a Pay-as-you-Go model.</p>\n<p>I was not as well aware of the feature until I logged in and started my launch of an application and server. Yes, it is, in fact, true… They actually do follow the motto</p>\n<p>“You will only be charged for what you consume.”</p>\n<p>You can scale your server size, your bandwidth, disk storage and much more. As you scale up your requirements, your pricing plan also increases and at each point you will know what your next invoice will be.</p>\n<h2>Unlimited Backups and Staging Environment</h2>\n<p>When we sought out to find the best hosting platform, we had a few things in mind. One which really kept us lingering on edge was which hosting platform will provide us backups and quick rollbacks, and we found Cloudways. You see Cloudways does not only offer it’s customers unlimited backups, but it also allows you to set the frequency of your backups as per your preferences. Ensuring that you will always have backups to roll back to when something goes wrong.</p>\n<p>Cloudways keeps the backups on a separate server, giving you a peace of mind even in the case you lose entire data on the server. Along with backups Cloudways let&#8217;s you create unlimited staging websites, you can also clone your live site to a staging site with just a click of a button! How cool is that! Also, it comes with a staging environment so you can test your website whenever you want before sending it out live across the Internet.</p>\n<h2>Free WordPress Migration</h2>\n<p>Most hosting providers offer a one time WordPress Migration absolutely free. So what makes Cloudways any different to other competitors and many reliable names? With Cloudways you get Free unlimited WordPress migrations.</p>\n<p>With the <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/bv-cloudways-automated-migration/">WordPress Migrator Plugin</a>, you can migrate a unlimited number of WordPress sites automatically to Cloudways in just a few minutes. It seems like they do know that manual migration is quite hectic. That’s why they have made the WordPress migrator plugin absolutely free and easy to use.</p>\n<h2>Install Free SSL Certificates With Just a Click and Top Notch Security</h2>\n<p>When it comes to hosting WordPress, security is one of the major factors that an individual may consider. Our exploration provided an insight that Cloudways has great security features. It comes with SSH and SFTP access to every server and application. So, rest assured that all communication channels in between websites and servers are encrypted and secured.</p>\n<p>Most hosting platforms do not provide SSL leaving out individuals hazy on how important is the encryption of your site. However, Cloudways offers <a href="https://www.cloudways.com/en/free-ssl-hosting.php">Free SSL Certificates</a> with a single click install for all websites. We advise that all WordPress clients should have SSL certification on their websites as a top notch priority.</p>\n<p>So that’s all there is to it, here is the complete wrap up of the exciting features that Cloudways offers its users in comparison to other competitors,</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A Pay-As-You-Go pricing system.</li>\n<li>Unlimited Applications.</li>\n<li>Staging Areas &amp; URL.</li>\n<li>24x7x365 Live Chat Support.</li>\n<li>HTTP2.</li>\n<li>Real Time Monitoring.</li>\n<li>Team Collaboration.</li>\n<li>Platform Level Firewalls.</li>\n<li>SSH &amp; SFTP Access.</li>\n<li>Git Deployment.</li>\n<li>Multiple Datacenters &amp; Add-ons.</li>\n<li>Cloudways API &amp; CloudwaysBot.</li>\n<li>Single Click Installations, Cloning, Domain Mapping, FREE SSL, Backup, Scaling &amp; Restore.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>However, for a greater insight, you may have to visit their official website, Cloudways.</p>\n<h2>Question Yourself! What are you really looking for?</h2>\n<p>So every time you sit on your laptop making yourself comfortable at a cafe or your workdesk, you may end up asking yourself whether your online business is in safer hands or not! Our answer is YES! with Cloudways it really is.</p>\n<p>Cloudways is a user-friendly hosting provider that makes hosting easy for all. It is affordable and provides you clarity when it comes to pricing. With Cloudways, you can design almost any kind of website you desire. No matter how vast the database of your website is or what enterprise level is your business at! Cloudways gives you an ultimate user experience, All in just a few number of clicks.</p>\n<p>We have teamed up with Cloudways WordPress Hosting to offer you an incredible deal. Cloudways is a Managed Cloud Hosting Platform that makes it easy to setup and configure your server on a number of different  cloud infrastructure providers like DigitalOcean, Kyup, Vultr, AWS, GCE. Get a high performance WordPress site running in minutes.</p>\n<p><a href="https://platform.cloudways.com/signup?coupon=SPCW15">Signup</a> for Cloudways hosting service using this coupon code <strong>SPCW15</strong> which gets you a $15 credit and after signing up also get a coupon code for 50% off on any SeedProd plugin.</p>\n<p>Hurry now and sign up today to get this incredible offer.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.seedprod.com/cloudways-managed-wordpress-hosting-provider-helps-maintain-sites-better/">Cloudways &#8211; A Managed WordPress Hosting Provider That Helps You Maintain Your Sites Better</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.seedprod.com">SeedProd</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:103:"https://www.seedprod.com/cloudways-managed-wordpress-hosting-provider-helps-maintain-sites-better/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;